WEBVTT

00:15:28.730 --> 00:15:30.744
when if this was another industry,

00:15:30.768 --> 00:15:33.327
we'd be holding their feet
to the fire on some stuff.

00:15:33.351 --> 00:15:36.015
And no, I'm not the anti-weed guy,

00:15:36.039 --> 00:15:37.647
I'm the pro-thought guy.

00:15:37.671 --> 00:15:38.848
So: think.

00:15:38.872 --> 00:15:41.278
I don't even care
if you're smoking when you do it,

00:15:41.302 --> 00:15:42.888
just so long as you're an adult.

00:15:42.912 --> 00:15:44.252
So long as you're an adult,

00:15:44.276 --> 00:15:45.563
just think.

00:15:46.657 --> 00:15:50.148
(Applause)